values: been trying not to be depressed as of late... but to no avail.... It just seems that no what ever I try to do it blows up in face.... like I can't be good enogh....so tonight I'm getting trashed... probably not the bes idea but hey... anyone got a better one?

well for the first time in my life I went to the county fair... belive it or not I actually enjoyed it! I had the oppertunity to pet the goats and sheep and eat REAL carnival style funnel cake.. yum... all in all i had a lot of fun! get back to you all later !

it's friday and getting ready to go to fair this evening.... I don't know what think of this becuase i haven't even been there... why should I feel so wierd about this you ask oh my brothers and sisters? my girlfriend... thats why.... it's apparently like some big deal with her... SOOOOO iWHAT!!!!! I'm like one of those new yourkers that never went to the statue of liberty. I have lived in and around fayetteville my entire life and never went to the fair. well i'm taking the plunge i'll post WTF happens when I get back.

This will not be one of THOSE blogs people loath to run across... the WE will be put back into the blog and the Me-to-ness shall be non-existant.
